        "TileImage": "$($repository daa6a057-d25c-488e-96e4-1a36aed4b994).Image",
        "Description": "Happy Holidays 47!\rWelcome to Mendoza\r\rYou&apos;ve got a new assignment courtesy of Don Yates, it turns out that the Boss himself couldn&apos;t follow up on his Head of  Security Juan Cortazar who has been plotting with the winemaker Gabriel Vargas to terminate the  Sangria Day festival which is soon to take place at the Don&apos;s estates, as you can see Yates found it out later and wants them to be removed permanently along with their bodyguards while you disguised as a Mecenary.\r\rGood Hunting",
